This package provides a behavior that can be applied to a button or load event that will swap a running xaml theme to one specified in the behavior.
Just add System.Windows.Interactivity and drag and drop the CannoliThemeChangerBehavior onto a button or other event causing FrameworkElement in Blend and set a target xaml to load.
FeedPackage.Title: Cannoli.ThemeChanger

FeedPackage.Description:
This package provides a behavior that can be applied to a button or load event that will swap a running xaml theme to one specified in the behavior.
Just add System.Windows.Interactivity and drag and drop the CannoliBorderlessWindowBehavior onto your window object in Blend.
Note: You can then style that window by altering the CannoliBorderlessWindowStyle.xaml
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: Added more robust error reporting when themes cannot be found. Added support for both absolute AND relative theme URI's
FeedPackage.Title: Cannoli.ThemeChanger
